<thead><tr><th>Community</th><th>Year</th><th>Result</th><th>What happened after</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td>Lockhart ISD</td><td>2024</td><td class="savings">61.2% yes</td><td>Enrollment tripled. ACC opened campus with trade labs.</td></tr>
